Parliament, Tuesday, 26 February 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Police will this afternoon continue with the consideration of the referral by the Speaker of the National Assembly on the Independent Police Investigative Directorate (IPID) Executive Director’s Term of Office. Details of the meeting are as follows: Date: Tuesday 26 February 2019
	Time: 14:15
	Venue: G26, National Assembly Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON POLICE, MR FRANCOIS BEUKMAN. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Malatswa Molepo (Mr)
	Parliamentary Communication Services
